verbs.description: The Supreme Court [V: is] heading into the final month of its term , facing decisions on gerrymandering , unions , gay rights , abortion and President Donald Trump 's travel ban . This term 's best - known case is a culture - war clash that pits equal rights for gay customers against a claim of religious liberty from a Christian store owner . It is one of three major cases that feature a " compelled speech " claim from conservatives who object to liberal state laws . The others involve union fees and California 's required disclosures for " crisis ...
